Choosing a Shooting Mode

# The Command and Function Dials

The roles of the command and Function dials vary with the mode.

# 5

|  | Front command dial | Rear command dial | Fn (function) dial |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
|  |  |  |  |
| AUTO (AUTO) | Auto/ Scene Position | Exposure compensation | Film simulation |
| P (PROGRAM AE) | Program shift | Exposure compensation | Film simulation |
| S (SHUTTER PRIORITY AE) | Shutter speed | Exposure compensation | Film simulation |
| A (APERTURE PRIORITY AE) | Aperture | Exposure compensation | Film simulation |
| M (MANUAL) | Aperture | Shutter speed | Film simulation |
| FILTER (FILTER) | Program shift | Exposure compensation | Filter selection |
| Vlog | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode |
| C1/C2/C3/C4 (CUSTOM) | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode |
| (MOVIE) | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode | Varies with exposure mode |
